OL,5, When Sharon Lees' son David left a     
OL,6, psychiatric unit, she said she warned  
OL,7, staff he was too unwell to come home.  
OL,9,FTen days later, he stabbed a man to    
OL,10,Fdeath who was out walking his dog      
OL,11,Fbecause of "the voices in his head".   
OL,13,FSharon is demanding a public apology   
OL,14,Ffrom Hywel Dda health board for both   
OL,15,Fher son and the family of the man he   
OL,16,Fkilled, Lewis Stone, saying it "could  
OL,17,F(and) should have been prevented".     
OL,19,FHywel Dda said confidential information
OL,20,Fprevented it publishing its report.    
